<div2 type="sub-section">
<ab>ward K bed 19</ab> <ab rend="circled">Arm</ab> <ab>David Coon,</ab> <ab>co. K. 37th N.Y.</ab>
<milestone unit="undeclared" rend="horbar-long-left"/>
<ab><add rend="insertion" place="supralinear">Mrs.</add> Eveline Ballou Sullivan</ab> <ab>Ashland co. Ohio</ab>
<milestone unit="undeclared" rend="horbar-short-left"/>
<ab>wounded in the left leg, below knee, flesh wound, at Chancellorsville Sunday 4th&#8212;&#8212;feeling pretty comfortable, has good care</ab>
</div2>

<pb xml:id="leaf013v" facs="uva.00053.026.jpg" type="verso"/>
<pb xml:id="leaf014r" facs="uva.00053.027.jpg" type="recto"/>

